#### {{ drug.molecular_formula }}:

The in vitro study proved the essential similarity of both the formulations as evident from the similarity factor of > 50% in all the dissolution media. The ratios for geometric least square means and 90% confidence intervals were within the acceptance criteria of 80% to 125% for log transformed C(max), {{ drug.molecular_formula }}(0-t) and {{ drug.molecular_formula }}(0-∞) for losartan. No statistically significant difference between the two treatments was observed for either of the safety parameters.
